## Repository Map

| Path | What lives here |
|------|-----------------|
| `/` | Entry HTML pages, `CNAME`, `robots.txt`, service worker |
| `src/` | ES modules: `pages/`, `components/`, `lib/`, `config/`, `tracker/`, `search/` |
| `styles/` | `global.css` (tokens) + `styles/pages/*.css` |
| `countries/` | Pre-generated country/city/karat/market pages |
| `content/` | Guides, FAQ, tools, social, news pages |
| `admin/` | Admin panel (Supabase GitHub OAuth) |
| `server/`, `server.js` | Node/Express backend (JWT + bcrypt + Helmet + rate limiting) |
| `scripts/node/` | Build, validation, audit, enrichment scripts |
| `scripts/python/` | Automation: gold poster, spike detector, Supabase client |
| `.github/workflows/` | CI, deploy, hourly post, newsletters, health/spike/uptime |
| `tests/` | node:test suites |
| `docs/` | Reference docs + master plan + proposal intake |
| `data/` | Runtime state: `gold_price.json`, `last_tweet_state.json`, shops |
| `supabase/` | Schema SQL, seed data, verification queries |

---

## Arabic / RTL Requirements

- All user-visible strings go through `src/config/translations.js`.
- Layouts must work with `dir="rtl"`. Test 360px minimum.
- Mirror chevrons, arrows, progress bars; preserve number formatting.
- Copy must read like natural Arabic, not English-shaped Arabic.

---

## Freshness & Data Source Labels

| State | When | Required label |
|-------|------|----------------|
| `live` | Fetched within 60s, healthy | Source + timestamp |
| `cached` | Served from cache/SW | `Cached · last updated <time>` |
| `delayed` | Provider lag > threshold | `Delayed · source <provider>` |
| `estimated` | Derived from spot | `Reference estimate · methodology` |
| `fallback` | Provider failed | `Fallback · last known <timestamp>` |
| `closed` | Market closed | `Market closed · resumes <time>` |

