## AI Agent Operating System

This repo has a layered AI instruction system:

| Layer | Where | When to use |
|-------|-------|-------------|
| **Always-on** | `AGENTS.md`, `.cursorrules`, `CLAUDE.md` | Every session |
| **Path-scoped** | `.github/instructions/*.instructions.md` | Touching matching files |
| **Skills** | `.github/skills/<skill>/SKILL.md` | Multi-step tasks |
| **Prompts** | `.github/prompts/*.prompt.md` | Starting a focused task |
| **Specialist agents** | `.github/agents/*.md` | Sub-agent personas |
| **Central docs** | `docs/AI_AGENT_*.md` | Maps, libraries, playbooks |

Key entry points:
- `docs/AI_AGENT_OPERATING_SYSTEM.md` — the map
- `docs/AI_PROMPT_LIBRARY.md` — pick a prompt
- `docs/AGENT_SKILL_LIBRARY.md` — pick a skill
- `docs/CURSOR_HANDOVER.md` — complete handover reference

